p.k: I See You Robin brings Starfire on a fake stakeout in an attempt to get a kiss while Cyborg and Beast Boy hold their own stakeout to discover Raven's dark secret.
p.d: Robin, Starfire, Cyborg, Beast Boy and Raven continue the fun in TEEN TITANS GO! with all-new comedic adventures, giving viewers a look at what life is really like as a teen super hero.
